ss="framer-2qw1od" data-framer-name="We are both so delighted that you are able to join us in celebrating what we hope will be one of the happiest days of our lives. The affection shown to us by so many people since our roka has been incredibly moving, and has touched us both deeply. We would like to take this opportunity to thank everyone most sincerely for their kindness. We are looking forward to see you at the wedding." data-framer-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p dir="auto" style="--font-selector:R0Y7WWFsZGV2aS1yZWd1bGFy;--framer-font-family:&quot;Yaldevi&quot;, &quot;Yaldevi Placeholder&quot;, sans-serif;--framer-font-size:20px;--framer-text-alignment:center;--framer-text-color:rgb(255, 255, 255)" class="framer-text">To help you feel at ease and enjoy every moment of the celebrations, we’ve gathered a few thoughtful details we’d love for you to know before the big day.</p></div></div><div class="framer-scd0c2" data-framer-name="Information"><div class="framer-7git8z-container" data-framer-name="Hashtag" name="Hashtag"><!--$--><div name="Hashtag" class="framer-4ruyN framer-17ap30v framer-v-17ap30v" data-framer-name="Desktop" style="height:100%;width:100%"><div class="framer-1uo5st5"><div class="framer-oiyef5"><div class="framer-1vp93cc" data-framer-name="ChatGPT Image Aug 20, 2025 at 02_43_47 PM 1"><div style="position:absolute;border-radius:inherit;corner-shape:inherit;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;left:0" data-framer-background-image-wrapper="true"><img decoding="async" width="1024" height="1536" sizes="(min-width: 1400px) 120px, (min-width: 810px) and (max-width: 1399.98px) 120px, (max-width: 809.98px) 118.57px" srcset="/framerusercontent.com/images/4t1aa7PACXoKhBZnZQ7i0Sc2aLo.png 682w,/framerusercontent.com/images/4t1aa7PACXoKhBZnZQ7i0Sc2aLo.png 1024w" src="/framerusercontent.com/images/4t1aa7PACXoKhBZnZQ7i0Sc2aLo.png" alt style="display:block;width:100%;height:100%;border-radius:inherit;corner-shape:inherit;object-position:center;objec